seller.description:
My greatest passion and strength is my drawing ability. I draw literally every day since I was a kid. I graduated from High School of Fine Arts and then Faculty of Arts at the Maria Curie University. Nowadays I work as a freelancer - character designer with over 15 years of experience. My style is mainly inspired by japanese anime & manga. I usually create digitally with some addition of traditional techniques. 
I'm so excited and happy to work with you!

reviews.comment: The artist's professionalism, combined with their undeniable talent, made this experience truly remarkable. This isn't just a gift for my friend but something they will treasure for years to come. I'm beyond satisfied with the outcome and would highly recommend their services to anyone looking for a deeply personal and beautifully crafted portrayal of themselves.

The art is exactly what I was looking for and more. I am so pleased with it and will recommend this service to other people as it looks amazing. I can't wait to use these on my channel! The seller okashy has great communication and helped me get what I was looking for. Very happy!

10/10 amazing work great attention to detail and great creativity helped our vision come to life in an amazing way highly recommend his work! Got it done a day early as well super fast response! If you want yourself drawn in dragon ball style this is your man!

I recently collaborated with Okashy for a portrait, and I'm happy to share a positive experience. 

I appreciate Okashy's dedication to deliver an amazing art. In the end, he successfully captured the essence and identity I was seeking in the portrait. The willingness to incorporate feedback and make necessary adjustments showcased his professionalism.

I'm pleased with the final outcome and would recommend Okashy to others looking for a talented artist who values client satisfaction. Looking forward to potential future collaborations!
Communicated great and was cool adding somethings I wanted after the first image he sent me. He also did it quickly.
